                    <span>As always, I loved listening to Eckhart. The guided "Gateways" are great but I feel the music was awful. I found it to be very irritating. I am sure I will not listen to the second CD that has the music on it again. There is music here and there on the first CD too and it would have been better had it been left out.</span>
                  
              
